  Clifton, an Earthling eager to escape the planet, finds himself trapped on a planet where people obsess over their achievements. He meets Ahasuerus, an elderly man who has never left Earth despite decades of dreaming of space, and offers him a chance to join Clifton on his mission to the star Rigel. Initially hesitant, Ahasuerus eventually agrees to join Clifton, defying orders to remain on Earth. Through their journey, the story explores themes of adventure, exploration, and the desire for something more in life.